reviews.review_text: One of the best.. shows from '91 and beyond.  Unfortunately, I missed this by one show, but caught two on this MSG run.  Any show with Shakedown, HSF and Dark Star is going to be off the chain--and this puppy delivers!!
Smokin' Great show and beautiful quality for an AUD. One thing to note is that the titles for "Lovelight" and "Crowd" are flipped. "Lovelight" comes before the encore.

Great musician showcase A very good show, not one of the greatest. I like it when Garcia really cuts loose and shreds, and he doesn't really do any of that here, but he might just be leaving some air space for Hornsby & Marsalis, which is definitely a good thing to do, and he sounds tight at least. Great AUD recording, clear and separated, but with enough crowd noise to let you know how awesome it was. Worth a download.
